{"tid":1790345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特別使錢技巧】洗米華向華強夫婦捐777萬撐7警 克警基金5年收逾2億","createTime":"2019-12-20T02:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T03:08:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"799baad21a440547478d894f4135f4932ea88954","tid":1790345,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191219/large/1576753981_6421.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576753981_6421.png&h=e28479d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一眾「善長」包括向華強（右起）、向太陳嵐及「洗米華」周焯華等。<br />\n<br />\n三大基金之一的警察福利基金，單於今年6月11日至7月18日計，就獲得超過1,630萬元捐款，當中最大筆的1,000萬元捐款，來自「香港友好協進會」，榮譽贊助人為前特首董建華和梁振英，由全國政協常委唐英年任會長，核心成員不乏一眾富豪，如李澤鉅、李家傑和林建岳等。至於「警察子女教育信託基金」及「警察教育及福利信託基金」，去年資產則分別達1.05億元及5,480萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警隊貴為「紀律部隊之首」，其餘紀律部隊收取的捐款可謂望塵莫及。三大基金去年捐款額達4,359萬元，但捐款收入排名第二的懲教署則只有174萬元，僅為警隊的不足4%，飛行服務隊去年更只收得3,300元捐款。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191219/60396604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60396604&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=2e0715c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60396604&h=dee84acd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191219/60396604</a>"},{"pid":"6a053070f559c78e73118004b230b796473f47a7","tid":1790345,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"黑社會撐警"},{"pid":"62514afda23fea8fdf3babe2510abea5cf4aad7b","tid":1790345,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"$3300<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a08224126009ee37f7818ac0d59165